# Redesign rules

- `packages/redesign` is deterministic: no LLM, network, browser, or Cursor SDK calls.
- Reconciliation must improve measured facts, especially readable foreground/background contrast.
- Only force foreground colors inside surfaces Tell also controls.
- `OfflineRedesignGenerator` should emit the same contrast-grounded CSS used by the live seam.
- Direction presets are `editorial`, `precision`, `warm-minimal`, and `bold-contrast`.
- `buildOverridesPatch` emits reviewable `tell-overrides.css` diffs; never writes files itself.
- Cursor-SDK-backed patch drafting stays in `apps/web/src/lib/cursor-redesign.ts` and must fall back to deterministic output.
